The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms that incorporate external memory, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). However, since the paper focuses on the use of deep learning in reinforcement learning, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG.
